Sawyer Sweeten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sawyer_Sweeten 0 Sawyer Storm Sweeten (May 12, 1995 – April 23, 2015) was an American child actor. He was best known for playing Geoffrey Barone on the sitcom Everybody Loves Raymond. He committed suicide by a self-inflicted gunshot wound to the head.
